Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils.messages

Class ClientBuildMessage

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.messages.ClientBuildMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientMessage, ControllerHandleable, Transmittable, java.io.Serializable
public class ClientBuildMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClientMessage, ControllerHandleable
This immutable class represents a command given by the player to make a worker build on a given cell.
